cake.name: Round Chocolate Truffle Cake
cake.description: The heavenly taste of this Choco Truffle Cake will even leave the hardest-to-please chocolate addicts tranquil in every sense. Prepared with three layers of relishing chocolate cream filled in between the soft stacks of chocolate cake, and adorned with beautiful chocolate icing and rich glaze chocolate coating, this one is just irresistible.

cake.name: Delicious Butterscotch Cake
cake.description: Butterscotch cake is always considered a delicious dessert for any occasion, no matter how small or large. The buttery goodness of this delicious cake is sure to make your mouth water. All you need is a special occasion to enjoy it! This is the perfect treat for anyone who loves butterscotch.

cake.name: Caramel Cake With Crunchy White Chocolate
cake.description: Tired of the same chocolate cake on every occasion? Try this scrummy new cake from Bakingo. The delicious caramel cake is covered with white frosting and decorated with swirly and tasty hard white chocolate. Getting three incredible flavours in one, now that's an offer you can not refuse.

cake.name: Tangerine Infused Round Glaze Cake
cake.description: The love for tangy tangerine need not end! Taste the scrumptious flavour of divine orange infused with the gentle aroma of vanilla and treat your taste buds to this round orange glazed cake. Perfect for celebratory occasions all year round, grab this delight for your loved ones right away!

cake.name: Creamy Round Shape Pineapple Cake
cake.description: Add a dash of excitement to your life with this exciting caramel cake cake from Bakingo. With Tasty caramel flavours, this cake is the perfect addition to any special occasion. Top with creamy frosting and chunks of white chocolate to make it look extra special. Easy to serve, cut and eat due to the user-friendly design, now you can enjoy a party dessert that everyone will love.

cake.name: Round Shape Butterscotch Cake
cake.description: Always and Forever Delight! This three layered moist and smooth cake filled with butterscotch chips and Vanilla cream is something not to be missed! Topped with Butterscotch glaze and brown chocolate flakes, adorned with scrumptious caramel dressing on the sides, it's time to feel the crunch!

cake.name: Swirled in Flavor Butterscotch Cake
cake.description: Take a break from regular-looking cakes and say yes to the Swirls of Flavor Pineapple Cake. It is a beautifully composed cake with shades of white, yellow, and dark brown. Pineapple is the main flavor and filling in the cake paired with a little bit of vanilla and small chocolate bars.

cake.name: Half Chocolate Half Vanilla Cake
cake.description: A toothsome treat for the sugar lovers who are just passionate about chocolate and relish the mushiness of cake. Made of two layers of impossibly moist chocolate filled with mushy rich cream, this cake carries the enticing aroma of Vanilla and sumptuousness of chocolate. On top of it, the cake is garnished with handcrafted white and brown chocolate.

cake.name: Assorted Fruit and Almond Cake
cake.description: Freshly baked Vanilla cake, Whipped cream and bountiful tropical fruits come together to create a treat that is even tastier than it looks. This combination of whipped cream and fresh fruit is a perfect start for any celebration and an enticing end to any meal.

cake.name: Birthday Chocolate Overload Pinata Cake
cake.description: Grab the most special birthday cake for celebrations of your loved oneâ€™s birthday this year with a gorgeous chocolate pinata cake! Crack this fun filled delight to get a bite off of a dense chocolate cake topped with colourful gems, two kitkat and two Ferrero Rochers. This year crack the cake open instead of cutting it! Note: Hammer will be given with the cake.
